<p>I'm trying to use gems <code>lazyhighcharts</code> and <code>fancybox2-rails</code>to add charts within a fancybox.</p>  <p>To display a highchart, the code is right from the lazyhighcharts gem doc create the @chart object in the controller and display it with something like:</p>  <pre><code>high_chart("myID", @chart) </code></pre>  <p>To display a fancybox I use something like:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;%= link_to "myLabel", myPath, class: "fancybox fancybox.ajax" %&gt;  </code></pre>  <p>What's the code to display the chart in the fancybox? If those two code snippets are simply combined on the same page, the fancybox displays empty and the chart is rendered into the underlying page.</p>